---
import Button from "../../components/elements/Button.astro";
import LocationSVG from "../../../public/location.svg?raw";
import AttendeeSVG from "../../../public/attendee.svg?raw";
import CalenderSVG from "../../../public/calender.svg?raw";
import CostSVG from "../../../public/cost.svg?raw";
import regIcon from "../../../public/regIcon.svg?raw";
---

<section
class="flex justify-between items-center sm:w-[1142px] w-auto sm:mx-[149px] mx-4 mt-16"
>
<div class="flex sm:flex-row flex-col">
  <!-- about section -->
  <div class="sm:w-[704px] w-auto sm:order-1 order-2 sm:mr-[86px]">
    <p class="text-xl font-medium mb-4 text-gray-500">About</p>
    <hr />
    <!-- about event content -->
    <div class="mt-4">
      <p class="text-base text-justify text-gray-500">
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Curabitur venenatis aliquam sem
        nec commodo. Quisque lobortis, felis at cursus mattis, ligula nulla tristique augue, non
        tristique dui sapien ut diam. Morbi nisi leo, aliquam id ligula quis, imperdiet
        tristique nunc. Phasellus at bibendum purus, sed tincidunt ipsum. Maecenas ante libero,
        tincidunt ac iaculis at, cursus eget nisl. Morbi in dictum felis. Phasellus dui felis,
        placerat in blandit vel, laoreet et ligula. Quisque pharetra risus eu nisl mollis,
        ultrices porttitor leo volutpat. Cras velit sem, ornare ut maximus vitae, malesuada ut
        mauris. Pellentesque scelerisque nisl quis dui imperdiet interdum. Proin purus quam,
        rhoncus imperdiet porta eget, maximus eget nisi. Donec vitae odio eu orci convallis
        vehicula in id ligula. Sed sit amet mi porta, eleifend turpis vitae, pretium ex.
        Suspendisse finibus dui ligula, id malesuada turpis faucibus in. Quisque tincidunt
        aliquam turpis vitae gravida. Duis efficitur vel sem id porttitor. Nam venenatis nunc ac
        ante blandit, mollis posuere erat scelerisque. Proin pretium tempus efficitur. Fusce
        commodo, diam non pellentesque tempus, dolor velit iaculis tortor, a tincidunt elit
        neque id diam. Donec luctus nulla ut justo mattis, in ultricies lectus sollicitudin.
        Pellentesque ac suscipit nisi. Sed neque leo, ullamcorper eu neque eget, faucibus
        consequat dolor. In viverra faucibus lacus sed consequat. Aliquam erat volutpat.
        Praesent et nibh at tellus imperdiet consequat. Sed felis metus, dapibus in gravida
        vehicula, pretium ut arcu. In condimentum nec magna non faucibus. Class aptent taciti
        sociosqu ad litora torquent per conubia nostra, per inceptos himenaeos.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- event details content for location, attendance, dates, and cost -->
  <div class="sm:w-[352px] w-[343px] h-[576px] sm:order-2 order-1">
    <p class="text-xl font-medium mb-4 text-gray-500">Event details</p>
    <hr class="mb-4" />
    <!-- Location -->
    <div class="flex items-center">
      <!-- using the icon component -->
      <Fragment set:html={LocationSVG} />

      <div class="ml-2 leading-6">
        <p class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-500">Location</p>
        <p class="font-normal text-gray-500">124, Johnson street, Asokoro, Abuja</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Attendance -->
    <div class="flex items-center mt-8">
      <!-- using the icon component -->
      <Fragment set:html={AttendeeSVG} />

      <div class="ml-2 leading-6">
        <p class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-500">Attendance</p>
        <p class="font-normal text-gray-500">Physical + Online</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Date & Time -->
    <div class="flex mt-8">
      <!-- using the icon component -->
      <Fragment set:html={CalenderSVG} />

      <div class="ml-2">
        <p class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-500">Date & Time</p>
        <div class="flex mt-2">
          <div class="mr-8">
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-700">From</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500">June 30th</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500">10:00 GMT +1</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-700">To</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500">July 3rd</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500">16:00 GMT +1</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Cost -->
    <div class="flex items-center mt-8">
      <!-- using the icon component -->
      <Fragment set:html={CostSVG} />

      <div class="ml-2 leading-6">
        <p class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-500">Cost</p>
        <p class="font-normal text-gray-500">Free</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex mt-8">
      <div class="w-[352px] text-center" id="custom-width">
        <Button href="#" label="Register" style="primary" size="md" />
      </div>
      <a
        href="#"
        class="inline-flex px-3 py-0 justify-center items-center"
      >
      <Fragment set:html={regIcon} />
      </a>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 pt-4">Registration open till June 28th 10:00 GMT +1</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</section>